# Normalize text files to LF across Windows, macOS, and Linux.
* text=auto eol=lf

# The Windows batch launchers must ship with CRLF so cmd.exe parses them. Keep their
# bytes verbatim (-text disables LF normalization) so the git blob — which the
# publication exporter ships as-is — carries CRLF for adopters on Windows.
/teami.cmd -text
/factory.cmd -text

# Binary assets should never be line-ending normalized.
*.avif binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.pdf binary
*.png binary
*.webp binary
*.zip binary
